{"tid":1794220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上周五大埔開槍案提堂　18歲少年還押至明年6月再訊","createTime":"2019-12-23T03:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T06:21:57.000Z","uid":57073,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"381629d3160163a8f25bae8a2e3a9c58ec704e00","tid":1794220,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:17:24.000Z","msg":"- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-23-2019/58521?fbclid=IwAR1_jqVoCueB14MiasZcCWUI0D_5VH-wHalW673ct61x6vRPHyfbuH1UjBs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F12-23-2019%2F58521%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1_jqVoCueB14MiasZcCWUI0D_5VH-wHalW673ct61x6vRPHyfbuH1UjBs&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=459d04fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-23-2019/58521?fbclid=IwAR1_jqVoCueB14MiasZcCWUI0D_5VH-wHalW673ct61x6vRPHyfbuH1UjBs</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019<br />\n<br />\n一名18歲男子上周五晚（12月20日）在大埔翠屏花園被截查期間，涉嫌向警員開一槍，他被控有意圖而射擊及無牌管有槍械或彈藥罪，今早（12月23日）在粉嶺裁判法院提堂。  被告暫時毋須答辯，案件押後至明年6月8日再訊，等候警方化驗報告，被告無申請保釋，要還押看管。  被告亦涉及本月8日警方於多處檢獲武器的案件，他被控一項串謀有意圖而傷人罪，案件押後至明年2月18日，於東區裁判法院與同案其他被告合併處理。"},{"pid":"d9c11dd1aeaa8e9daa7735a1e5e8d8897f536e70","tid":1794220,"uid":57073,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:18:54.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n老屈 還押半年 仆街"},{"pid":"967e406b64cfb71454ddc8a5c3f71402adb21b0d","tid":1794220,"uid":114487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VgwZ4tD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVgwZ4tD.jpg&h=52b479a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGepv8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGepv8D.jpg&h=265d7544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocgLfAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocgLfAm.jpg&h=e2a8e121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":